288
00:17:20,810 --> 00:17:25,950
Wataru-kun, it's not Tama, but a real beast hiding there.

289
00:17:28,530 --> 00:17:29,430
You idiot!

290
00:17:32,740 --> 00:17:33,800
Sir!

