00:17:36,730 --> 00:17:37,780
Sir!

293
00:17:40,680 --> 00:17:41,580
Saki.

294
00:17:43,520 --> 00:17:44,770
Katsura-sensei!

295
00:17:46,000 --> 00:17:48,780
